Today’s Volunteer event with @comfortcases and @rob_scheer was amazing. It feels  so good to give back to those in need. We spent our morning packing backs for foster children and also got to meet @drewsidora

What an action-packed day in Atlanta for the #GeorgiaTakeoverProgram with our partners @amerigroup3 🙌💙🎒

Some good humans and our dear friends @drewsidora, @caras_atl & @stroudgang_ joined us! These good humans are not only helping us spread the word of this program via social media, but they are also getting hands-on, packing #ComfortCases…and that’s what it’s all about! 🫶🤩

The partnership between Amerigroup Georgia and Comfort Cases marks a historic moment in the nation’s efforts to support children in the foster care system. The first-of-its-kind initiative showcases the power of collective action and sets an inspiring precedent for other states to follow. Through this partnership, Amerigroup Georgia is committed to ensuring that every child in Georgia’s foster care system knows they matter by providing them with a Comfort Case and bringing dignity and hope to our most vulnerable youth. 🫶🎒

Please help us bring dignity and hope to children entering foster care and help us eliminate trash bags! 

Go to https://comfortcases.org/amerigroupgatakeover/ for more info on how you can participate!
